{
  "texts": [
    "A content expert, who is an experienced teacher, took role of an outside source and analyzed the lesson plans based on content suitability and educational applicability.",
    "The same prompts were entered to the chatbots another time to assure trustworthiness of the data.",
    "Ethical issues such as privacy, fairness and non-discrimination, transparency in the use of chatbots have been brought up to attention by the researchers (Cotton et al., 2023; Mhlanga, 2023).",
    "In the data collection process of this study, however, no ethical rules were violated when using the chatbots.",
    "This section addresses the first research question: 'Are there any differences among generative AI applications in developing lesson plans?\""
  ]
}